highlights.text: Annika has the most spots on Top Songs Denmark. “Stolt (feat. Lamin)” is the highest at #6.
“Fire Uger” by Mumle is the highest new entry on Top Songs Denmark at #26.
“555 (feat. KESI)” by Gilli and KESI has been on Top Songs Denmark the longest, at 98 weeks straight.
“Sports car” by Tate McRae is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Denmark, up 69 spots at #119.
